'''''Heroes''''' is an album by American pianist [[David Benoit (musician)|David Benoit]] released in 2008, and recorded for the Peak label. The album is Benoit's tribute to his musical 'heroes' who influenced his career, including [[Bill Evans]], [[Dave Brubeck]], and [[Dave Grusin]].<br/>
''Heroes'' reached #9 on ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'''s contemporary Jazz chart.

